query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_link AS ml JOIN link_type AS lt ON lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('sequel', 'follows', 'followed by') JOIN title AS t2 ON t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND t2.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN kind_type AS kt2 ON kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND kt2.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN title AS t1 ON t1.id = ml.movie_id JOIN kind_type AS kt1 ON kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND kt1.kind IN ('tv series', 'episode') JOIN (SELECT it1.id AS it1_id, mi_idx1.info_type_id AS mi_idx1_info_type_id, mi_idx1.movie_id AS mi_idx1_movie_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1 JOIN info_type AS it1 ON it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'rating') AS it1_mi_idx1 ON t1.id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id AND ml.movie_id = it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id JOIN (SELECT mi_idx2.movie_id AS mi_idx2_movie_id, mi_idx2.info_type_id AS mi_idx2_info_type_id, it2.id AS it2_id FROM movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2 JOIN info_type AS it2 ON it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating' AND mi_idx2.info < '3.5') AS it2_mi_idx2 ON t2.id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc2 ON t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND it2_mi_idx2.mi_idx2_movie_id = mc2.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn2 ON cn2.id = mc2.company_id JOIN movie_companies AS mc1 ON t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it1_mi_idx1.mi_idx1_movie_id = mc1.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn1 ON cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND cn1.country_code <> '[us]'
label: 33c
